{"id":257715,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-浙江百余名市民集会抗议政府上马化工项/","date":"2012-10-17T11:01:00Z","modified":"2012-10-27T23:12:08Z","title":"维权网 | 浙江百余名市民集会抗议政府上马化工项目（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日上午</span><span>，浙江省宁波市镇海区政府门口，有百余市民集会抗议政府即将上马的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PX</span><span>化工厂项目，区政府信访办大门紧锁，众多特警到场，据目击者称有人被抓走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-066HjdXtPew/UH5oWisyN-I/AAAAAAAARVg/nJsPj1ELHYo/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"242\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-066HjdXtPew/UH5oWisyN-I/AAAAAAAARVg/nJsPj1ELHYo/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，当地市民得知宁波镇海将要上马投资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>亿元的化工项目，使宁波的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PX</span><span>项目产能增加到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>万吨。根据宁波市“十一五”规划纲要，在此期间的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PX</span><span>产能要达到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>万吨。镇海炼化</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PX</span><span>项目现在已拥有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>万吨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span><span>年芳烃生产能力。按国际惯例，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PX</span><span>项目应建在远离城市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>公里</span><span>之外，镇海炼化的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PX</span><span>项目距宁波老城区只有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>公里</span><span>，距新城</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>公里</span><span>，距镇海</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>公里</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>有当地居民表示，要坚决抵制</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PX</span><span>项目，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GDP</span><span>换不来健康，换不来幸福，换不来山清水秀。不要因为我们觉得自己声音小就不发出自己的声音，我们要大声的说不要污染。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>，有宁波居民反映，当地政府的和事业单位领导都开会通知了，要求大家保持沉默。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-8569137480581934991?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[20764,8906,19196]}